Tweak'd by Nature Supersize Amber Vanilla Restore Shampoo/Conditioner

What It Is 
The perfect supersize set for beautiful hair.

What You Get 


    33.8 fl. oz. Dhatelo Restore Hair Strengthening Shampoo
    33.8 fl. oz. Dhatelo Restore Hair Strengthening Conditioner 


What It Does

Dhatelo Restore Hair Strengthening Shampoo


    Instantly helps cleanse and moisturize while helping to revitalize damaged hair 
    Gently cleanses with naturally derived cleansing agents and Tweakd's Plant4FOAM complex 
    Gently removes product residue and debris without stripping away the hair and scalp of their natural oils 
    Preps the hair for Tweak'd by Nature conditioners, cleansing treatments and styling products 
    Moisturizing and conditioning properties to optimize the hair's elasticity


Dhatelo Restore Hair Strengthening Conditioner 


    Instantly helps hydrate and revitalize damaged hair 
    This rich formula infuses hair with essential lipids 
    Protects against heated styling tools 
    Helps to optimize the hair's elasticity to reduce hair breakage
